  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK782">
<l>niṟainīra nīravar kēṇmai piṟaimatip</l>
<l>piṉṉīra pētaiyār naṭpu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The friendship of the wise waxes like the new moon (but) that of fools wanes like the full moon.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
